Class DollarCostStockImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.DollarCostStockImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DollarCostStrategy, HigherLevelStrategy
    public class DollarCostStockImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements DollarCostStrategy
    This class represents stocks created using dollar costing average strategy. In this strategy, the user creates a portfolio of stocks and determines their relative proportion. Then the user invests a fixed amount of money in this portfolio at regular frequency over a long period of time.
